213
00:17:21,090 --> 00:17:24,110
However, President Yue has not changed his mind.

214
00:17:24,110 --> 00:17:27,180
I bet that Miss Gu's isn't feeling so well now.

215
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:29,770
