237
00:19:56,620 --> 00:19:58,640
When did I...?

238
00:20:00,530 --> 00:20:02,660
<i>Sister Xin'er!</i>

239
00:20:08,440 --> 00:20:12,020
<i>Lower your voice. People will hear your voice.</i>

240
00:20:12,020 --> 00:20:14,850
<i>Just pretend you didn't see what happened today. Understood?</i>

241
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:16,580
<i>Or else I will...</i>

242
00:20:19,100 --> 00:20:22,080
<i>-Why are you here?
-I'm waiting for my brother to finish class.</i>

243
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:24,330
